column2: W: wire,  nn: gauge,  n: number of conductors, C or R: cotton or rayon braid, 1 letter: style of wire, 2 letters: color #1, 2 letters: color #2 or XX if there isn't a second color, S or F or L: S is normal-sized  spool for the wire, F is by the foot, L is 50-foot spool
So W182CTBKXXS is 18/2 cotton twisted black by the 250-foot spool
